": "776.0", "version_code": 11997, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 73}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "2412327085529357", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8737583633003639"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1734139763, "id": "8744706085624727", "version": "776.0", "version_code": 11990, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 73}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "2412327085529357", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8737583633003639"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2309851355956647"}]}, "change_log": "New Update v775.0\n\nUpdates\nNew Players: We have moved the first time player onboarding experience from Cliffs to TPC Scottsdale.\nRatings: In-game button to leave a star rating. Leaving a rating has a huge impact for us! Thank you for your support!\n\nQuality and Bug Fixes\nBattle Mode: Fixed the target circle on course screen displaying in the wrong spot for battle playoffs.\nTournaments: Depending on how the player left the round, after resuming a round and finishing the hole, the score for the hole could be miscounted.\nPerformance: Improved performance related to new golf bags and avatars.\n\nNew GOLF+ Tour Season\nThe 2025 Spring season will begin with a 'soft reset' that reduces all players' points by 50%. The top 30 players receive an additional point reduction to promote competition in Diamond tier. Ranks and tiers stay the same for all players. \n\nThe Spring Season will run for 4 months, concluding with the Spring Championship on April 16th, 2025. \n\nWhat is a GOLF+ TOUR Season?\nFor those new to the GOLF+ TOUR, each season spans 4 months and includes regular tournaments and elevated majors, culminating in a championship event. The seasonal cadence ensures fresh opportunities for competition and progression.\n\nWorld Rankings\nIntroducing the new 'World Rankings,' designed to give a long-term view of the GOLF+ Tour. Spanning 26 weeks (6 months), World Rank offers a broader perspective and isn't impacted by the seasonal points resets. At this time, World Rankings are available exclusively on the website.\n\nTrophies & Badges\nTrophies and season badges for season finish will be awarded during the weekly rollover.", "created_date": 1734028928, "id": "8737583633003639", "version": "775.0", "version_code": 11976, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 71}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "2412327085529357", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8737583633003639"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1733953433, "id": "8732650013497001", "version": "775.0", "version_code": 11966, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 71}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "b